title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 §§ 197-3.17 - Continuing education credit
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 §§ 197-3.17 - Continuing education credit

State Regulations

No continuing education course will be considered for
continuing education credit more than once within the two-year cycle of
renewal. Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19
§§
197-3.17

State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
